</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>If the girl prepared onion soup in her dream and then ate it, this is a good indication of her recovery from health problems and improvement of her financial situation, as she enjoys good company that represents support and support for her in all difficult situations and happy occasions. This may be represented in her imminent marriage to the young man she desires as a life partner.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of seeing vegetable soup in a dream for a single woman</strong></h2>
<p>Interpreters have pointed to the good tidings of seeing a single girl vegetable soup, because it is a symbol of courage and the multiplicity of blessings in her life. The dream also confirms the death of the hardships and pains that she goes through.  And she wishes that the next one will be full of happiness and prosperity and the fulfillment of goals and desires by the will of God. In case of fear or hesitation in something, she should abandon these negative feelings and be bold and decisive.  To achieve what it aspires to.</p>
<p>Seeing soup in the girl's dream is an indication of success and excellence in her academic life, in case she is a science student, which makes her obtain the required academic qualification. But emotionally, she will have a new good man who will provide her with happiness and prosperity. And she will find in him a responsible father for her children in the future, God willing.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
