</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>As for her feeling of emotional emptiness and loneliness at this stage of her life, due to her husband's ill-treatment and the outbreak of many disputes and quarrels between them, then her vision of a plate of soup is considered a praiseworthy sign of the disappearance of her husband's. The worries and problems she goes through and the improvement of the situation between them, so that her husband will care for her and care for her as he was in the past. This is due to her patience and rationality to overcome difficulties and her desire to maintain her home and provide security for her children.</p>
<h2><strong>Eating soup in a dream for a married woman</strong></h2>
