<p>Fingers in a dream symbolize children, parents, money, and other interpretations. We will translate them for single women, married women, pregnant women, divorced women, and men, such as long fingers, cut fingers, or cut fingers.  Excess fingers, a man's finger or a man's foot, and seeing the index finger cut off, a child's finger, for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" >Ibn Sirin</a> and others, in continuation of the topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Fingers in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Fingers in a dream mean <strong>children, spouses, parents, mothers, money, possessions, and everything that helps a person in his world. Whoever sees an increase in his fingers, then an increase in what we have mentioned, and vice versa, a decrease is a decrease.  And a defect in what was mentioned is the death of animals or the loss of a source of profit, such as a decline in trade or industry.</strong></p>
<p>The thumb: <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الظهر-في-المنام?page=2782" >Zuhr prayer</a>, the index finger: Asr prayer, the middle finger: <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-العشاء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=826" >Isha prayer</a>, the middle finger: prayer after death, and the little finger: <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الفجر-في-المنام?page=3211" >Fajr prayer</a> for brevity.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
