</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Fingers in a dream may indicate the five prayers, and the nails are their time.</p>
<p>Seeing <strong>the thumb in a dream</strong> indicates morning, the index finger until noon, the middle finger until noon, the middle finger indicates sunset, and the little finger indicates <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-العشاء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=826" >Isha prayer</a>.</p>
<p>And if the fingers are money, then the nails are zakah.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
