</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>The length of the finger in a dream indicates greed.</p>
<p>The appearance of an extra finger on his fingers is an increase in money, kinship, prayer, or work.</p>
<p>Moving a finger from one place to another may indicate <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تأخير-الصلاة-في-المنام?page=1456" >delaying prayer</a></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
