<p><span></span><span></span></p>
<p>Interlocked fingers may indicate a gathering for prayer or a gathering of relatives about a matter that concerns the dreamer</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>It can indicate a handshake or marriage and a contract, and it can indicate slowness in <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-أداء-الصلاة-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3623" >performing prayer</a>.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
