<p><span></span></p>
<p>And <strong>the fingers of the right hand</strong>, the five prayers, and their brevity indicate negligence in prayer and laziness in it, and the length of the fingers indicates the persistence of prayer, and the breaking of one of them may indicate the abandonment of prayer.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>And <strong>the fingers of the left hand</strong> can refer to daughters or sisters.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
