</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p>And seeing the biting of others' fingers indicates a bad character in the person.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>The fingers of a man are drawn with henna in a dream, which indicates a lot of praise. As for the woman, this dream indicates her husband's love for her. If the woman puts henna on her fingers and it is not visible, then this dream indicates that her husband hides his love for her.</p>
<p><span></span><span></span></p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
