</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Fingers in a Dream for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" >Ibn Sirin</a></span></h2>
<p>The <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/مترجم-الأحلام-محمد-بن-سيرين?page=3415" >Dream Interpreter Muhammad ibn Sirin</a> says that the finger in a dream indicates the things that help a person in his world and the things that help you in work. The finger in a dream indicates a son, spouse, father, mother, money, or wealth. Whoever sees that his fingers have grown large, then this is good, for this indicates an increase in money and livelihood, and a decrease in money.<br/>Perhaps the cutting off of a finger in a dream indicates that you will not benefit from the father or from the mother or from the children, or it indicates that the money will go away, or that his work will be disrupted, or that his trade will fail.</p>
<p>Fingers may indicate the king's deputies, who differ in their ranks and advantages. Whoever sees himself biting his fingers in a dream, then his disease will die.<br/>And whoever sees his fingers cut off or infected with some disease, this indicates weakness in his soldiers or children, or relatives or acquaintances.<br/>Perhaps fingers refer to the five prayers, so the thumb is for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الفجر-في-المنام?page=3211" >Fajr prayer</a>, the index finger is for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الظهر-في-المنام?page=2782" >Zuhr prayer</a>, the middle finger is for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-العشاء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=826" >Isha prayer</a>, the middle finger is at sunset, and the little finger is for Isha. He said: "The middle one is for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الفجر-في-المنام?page=3211" >Fajr prayer</a> because it is recommended to lengthen it, and the little finger is for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-صلاة-الظهر-في-المنام?page=2782" >Zuhr prayer</a>, and the little finger is for Asr prayer because it is the end of the day. And if the fingers are money, then the nails are zakah, and if the fingers are soldiers, then the nails are weapons and their number.</p>
<p>And the fingers hold money, and the fingers are days or months or years. Perhaps the fingers refer to the children of the brother and the shoulder is the brother.  And the fingers are in the state of the children and they are money.<br/>Whoever sees that his finger is cut off and then his money is harmed, and what is done with the fingers of righteousness or corruption is related to duty or to the brother, and the length of the fingers indicates an increase.  In greed.<br/>If he sees a finger that grew on his fingers, then this is an increase in his relatives, in his prayer, or in his knowledge.<br/>And if he sees that one of his fingers has moved to another place, then he delays prayer for the next time.<br/>Whoever sees: that he folded his fingers, then he gathered his prayers together.  Perhaps his relatives have gathered together for a matter to consult and cooperate, and it is said that the fingers are interlocked without working with them with a handclasp, and it is said that they indicate connection, or closeness and compactness.  Perhaps this indicates the cancellation of movement and prayer.  And it is said: The fingers of the right hand are the five prayers, and their shortening indicates negligence and laziness in them, and their length indicates the persistence of prayer, and the fall of one of them indicates the abandonment of prayer.<br/>Whoever sees: as if he had bitten a man's fingernails, then this indicates the bad behavior of the one who bit him.<br/>Whoever sees: as if milk comes out of his thumb, and blood comes out of his index finger and he drinks from them, then he is on his wife's mother or sister, and breaking the fingers indicates the occurrence of bad words. From his relatives.<br/>And if the imam sees an increase in his fingers, then this indicates an increase in greed and oppression and the absence of justice, and the fingers of the left hand are the children of the brother and sister, and drawing the fingers of men with henna indicates a lot. Praise, and drawing the fingers of a woman with henna indicates the kindness of her husband to her, and her husband does not show his love for her.</p>
