<h2><span>Interpretation of the Dream of Fingers for Al-Osaimi</span></h2>
<p>The scholar Sheikh Al-Osaimi explained <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأصابع-في-المنام?page=3687" >seeing fingers</a> in a dream with different details and meanings determined by the character of the visionary, including a lot of praise and the five prayers.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأصابع-في-المنام?page=3687" >broken fingers</a> in a dream means bad words coming from relatives in the family for whoever sees it</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Cutting Fingers in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>The meanings of seeing a person cutting a finger for the dreamer in a dream indicate the loss of money or work. It is said that it is sadness and worry, and God knows best.<br/>Seeing <strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-جرح-إصبع-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=87" >a finger injury</a> in a dream</strong> for all indicates the loss of property and possessions, or the death of animals, and the loss of trade.  It has been said that it is the death of the sick, and God knows best.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Interlocked Fingers in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>The meanings of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأصابع-في-المنام?page=3687" >seeing interlocked fingers</a> in a dream for all indicate praiseworthy meanings, including cooperation in work from a private project or trade for whoever sees it.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الأصابع-في-المنام?page=3687" >interlocked fingers</a> in dreams indicates kinship and marriage for whoever sees it, and God knows best.</p>
