<h2><span>Interpretation of Fingers in a Married Woman's Dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a wife's fingers adorned with henna in a dream symbolizes affection and love between the spouses and the husband's good treatment of her, and God knows best.<br/>The meanings of seeing a woman's fingers with henna that is not attached to her in a dream indicate the husband's neglect and lack of attention to his wife, and God knows best.<br/>The vision shows <strong>the fingers of the left hand in the married woman's dream</strong> to the children of the brother whom she sees, and God knows best.<br/>Seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الجرح-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=194" >a wound</a> in the wife's dream symbolizes separation or the loss of someone from the family, and God knows best.</p>
